It's alright.

* The voltures glanced towards Rion as he came bounding over the sandhill, 
cocking their heads towards him, a few others still picking at the mass of 
fur between them all.
But then they raies into the air and began to squak as Rion fired his 
cannon, their mind swimming in panic.


Diana looked up at the flutter of feathers, seeing some bird bot between 
them. But she couldn't make it out until the birds had lifted off.
She looked up and watched the raptors circle a bit still, wondering if they 
would come in again.
She hoped not.
She then looked over at the bird/bot, getting to her feet and shaking 
herself. Mewing when she felt where the scratches were on her body from her 
attacjers sharp beaks.
Diana looked at the bleeding scratches, nothing seriouse.
She then looked at the boy bot...around ger age.
Who...her scanners read that...it...was..Rion?
She took a slightly shaky step towards him.*

" Rion?"

* Her voice was a hopefup mew.*
